=== Fluid Type Identification from Field Data
<fluid-type-identification-from-field-data>
In practice, fluid type is identified from:

+ #strong[Initial producing GOR] --- measured at the test separator
+ #strong[Stock tank oil gravity (API)] --- from sample analysis
+ #strong[Reservoir temperature and pressure] --- from well logs and DST data
+ #strong[C$""_(7 +)$ fraction] --- higher C$""_(7 +)$ content indicates heavier fluid
+ #strong[Visual observation] --- color of separator liquid (clear/straw = condensate; brown/black = oil)

