=== Casing Design per API 5C3
<casing-design-per-api-5c3-1>
The mechanical design calculation follows API Bull 5C3 for casing strength:

#strong[Burst rating:]

$ P_(b u r s t) = frac(0.875 times 2 times Y_p times t, D_o) $

#strong[Collapse rating] (for the yield strength collapse regime):

$ P_(c o l l a p s e) = 2 times Y_p (frac(D_o \/ t - 1, \( D_o \/ t \)^2)) $

#strong[Tension rating:]

$ F_(t e n s i o n) = Y_p times A_s $

where:

- $Y_p$ is the minimum yield strength \[psi\]
- $t$ is the wall thickness \[in\]
- $D_o$ is the outer diameter \[in\]
- $A_s$ is the cross-sectional area of the pipe body \[in²\]

Design factors per NORSOK D-010:

