=== Effect of Flow Rate on Pressure Drop
<effect-of-flow-rate-on-pressure-drop>
The relationship between flow rate and pressure drop is nonlinear. At low rates, gravitational effects dominate in inclined pipes. At high rates, friction dominates:

```python
