=== Saturation Index
<saturation-index>
The saturation index (SI) indicates the tendency for scale formation:

$ S I = log_10 (Q_(i o n) / K_(s p)) $

where:

- $Q_(i o n)$ is the ion activity product of the scaling species
- $K_(s p)$ is the solubility product at the given T, P conditions

