Scale inhibitor deployment methods: - #strong[Continuous injection] via chemical injection line (most common topside) - #strong[Squeeze treatment] --- inhibitor is adsorbed onto the formation rock and slowly released during production (preferred for subsea wells) - #strong[Scale inhibitor in drilling/completion fluids] --- provides early-life protection

