A traffic-light color scheme is typically used:

- #strong[Green] ($U < 80 %$): Normal operation with adequate spare capacity
- #strong[Yellow] ($80 % lt.eq U < 95 %$): Approaching limit --- monitor closely
- #strong[Red] ($U gt.eq 95 %$): At or near capacity limit --- action required

