=== Role of VFP Tables in Well Allocation
<role-of-vfp-tables-in-well-allocation>
VFP tables serve two roles in well allocation:

+ #strong[In the network solver.] The `LoopedPipeNetwork` uses VFP tables (or the underlying tubing model) to determine the flowing pressures and deliverability of each well at the current network conditions.
+ #strong[In reservoir simulation.] VFP tables allow the reservoir simulator to quickly evaluate well deliverability without re-running multiphase flow calculations, enabling efficient long-term forecasting.

The accuracy of VFP tables depends on the resolution of the tabulated parameters and the quality of the underlying multiphase flow model. For wells with complex trajectories, severe slugging, or unusual fluid properties, higher-resolution tables or direct coupling to the flow model may be needed.

