WCONPROD
-- Well    Status  Mode   Rate   Resv   BHP    THP   VFP#
  'PROD-1'  OPEN   ORAT   5000   1*     100    30     1   /
  'PROD-2'  OPEN   ORAT   3000   1*     100    40     1   /
/
