=== Results
<results>
After six months of Level 2 operation, the digital twin identified:

+ #strong[Compressor efficiency degradation] of 5% due to blade fouling --- justified an early maintenance intervention
+ #strong[Suboptimal LP separator pressure] --- reducing from 8 to 5 bara increased condensate recovery by 2.3%
+ #strong[Heat exchanger fouling] --- UA reduced by 30% over 4 months, triggering a cleaning campaign

The combined production improvement was approximately 3.5%, equivalent to \$25 million per year for this facility.

