=== Economic Optimization
<economic-optimization>
The objective function for plant optimization balances NGL revenue against operating costs:

$ max quad J = sum_i V_i dot.op P_i - C_(upright("fuel")) dot.op E_(upright("fuel")) - C_(upright("power")) dot.op W_(upright("total")) - C_(upright("chemicals")) $

subject to:

$ y_(upright("H")_2 upright("S")) & lt.eq 4 upright(" ppmv")\
y_(upright("CO")_2) & lt.eq 2 upright(" mol%")\
w_(upright("water")) & lt.eq 50 upright(" mg/Sm")^3\
upright("Product purities") & gt.eq upright("specifications")\
upright("Equipment capacities") & lt.eq upright("design limits") $

where $V_i$ and $P_i$ are product volumes and prices, $E_(upright("fuel"))$ is fuel gas consumption, $W_(upright("total"))$ is total power consumption, and $C$ denotes unit costs.

