=== Process Description
<process-description>
The production system consists of:

- #strong[Subsea gathering]: Four wells produce into a common manifold, then through a 12 km subsea flowline to the platform riser base
- #strong[HP separator]: Operates at 80 bara, separating gas, condensate, and water
- #strong[LP separator]: Operates at 15 bara, further degassing the HP condensate
- #strong[1st stage recompressor]: Compresses LP gas from 15 to 30 bara
- #strong[2nd stage recompressor]: Compresses from 30 to 55 bara
- #strong[3rd stage recompressor]: Compresses from 55 to 80 bara (rejoins HP gas)
- #strong[TEG dehydration]: Dehydrates the combined gas to pipeline spec
- #strong[Export compressor]: Boosts gas from 80 to 180 bara for pipeline export
- #strong[Condensate stabilizer]: Atmospheric-pressure flash to meet condensate vapor pressure specification
- #strong[Export pipeline]: 200 km pipeline to shore at 180 bara

