$ 2 upright("H")_2 upright("O") arrow.r 2 upright("H")_2 + upright("O")_2 quad Delta H = + 286 upright(" kJ/mol") $

The three main electrolysis technologies are:

#figure(
  align(center)[#table(
    columns: 5,
